}

### Auth: Profile (requires token)
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Users: List (admin)
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Tour Packages: List (public)
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/tour-packages?page=1&limit=10

### Bookings: Create (user)
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "destination": "Cebu",
  "startDate": "2025-01-10",
  "endDate": "2025-01-12",
  "travelers": 2,
  "totalPrice": 15000,
  "type": "CUSTOMIZED",
  "tourType": "PRIVATE",
  "itinerary": [
    {
      "dayNumber": 1,
      "activities": [
        {
          "time": "09:00",
          "title": "Arrival",
          "order": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### Bookings: Add collaborator (owner)
