Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "collab@example.com"
}

### Bookings: List collaborators (owner or collaborator)
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/bookings/{{bookingId}}/collaborators
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

